Installation:
-------------

1) Linux:

download splunk .tgz package or wget
tar xvzf splunk.tgz -C /opt
cd /opt/splunk/bin

./splunk start --accept-license
./splunk stop
./splunk restart
./splunk help

set username and pwd

2) Windows: Download a gui


3) For OSX: use .dmg
Applications/splunk/bin




